TC-016 – Validate successful checkout completion

Preconditions: User has a product in the shopping cart.

Steps:

1. Click the "Checkout" button.
2. Fill in the required fields (First Name, Last Name, and Zip/Postal Code) with valid information.
3. Click the "Continue" button.

Expected Result:
The system should display an order summary page containing product information (name, description, and price), payment information, shipping information, and the total purchase amount.

Actual Result:
The system displayed the summary page with all expected information.

Status: Passed.

TC-017 – Validate order completion

Preconditions: User has a product in the shopping cart.

Steps:

1. Click the "Checkout" button.
2. Fill in the required fields with valid information.
3. Click the "Continue" button.
4. Click the "Finish" button.

Expected Result:
The system should display a page informing that the order was completed successfully, along with the option to generate a PDF containing the order information.

Actual Result:
The system displayed a message informing the order completion and provided the option to generate a PDF with the order information.

Status: Passed.
